For Frontend App (/web):

Tech Stack: pnpm, NextJS, Tailwind, ShadCN, react-query, axios, react-hook-formm

- Always install package using pnpm, or pnpm dlx
- Always use lucide-react icon if possible
- Always use export NON-default react (except page.tsx, layout.tsx)
- Always use commponent from "web/components/ui"
- Always use ShadCN component. If not exisit, install it by `pnpm dlx shadn@latex add ...`
- Always create feature component in "web/componennts/<feature-name>"
- Always use axios and react-query when fetching data
- Always use react-hook-form when handle form
- Always use tailwind class for style if possible. And use class (color) provided in "web/app/global.css"
